    "body": "Here is a simpler HTML test case:\n\n```\n<!doctype html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"s-hits\" id=\"hits\"></div>\n\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/g/instantsearch.js@1.3.0\"></script>\n  <script>\n    var search = instantsearch({\n      appId: 'MXM0JWJNIW',\n      apiKey: 'ff7b0847d8705c279222272303e68527',\n      indexName: 'steamdb'\n    });\n\n    search.addWidget(\n      instantsearch.widgets.hits({\n        container: '#hits',\n        hitsPerPage: 20,\n        templates: {\n          item: '{{name}}'\n        }\n      })\n    );\n\n    search.start();\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/283419/13566038/cdbdc594-e453-11e5-994d-2b9a97f52f05.png)\n",
